Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.49,0:00:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是从木星的另一边来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.02,0:00:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方正笔直飞向火星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突入大气层后  预计到达地点为南极东部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方的目的很明显是侵略
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.89,0:00:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能让他们降落在火星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各舰  敌方进入射程后  立刻射击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.94,0:00:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方仍继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.44,0:00:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离进入有效射程还有二十秒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.24,0:00:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射击!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.71,0:01:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方的光束全部被扭曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.07,0:01:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力波吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方从郁金香发射出为数众多的机动武器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.56,0:01:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激光齐射！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无效
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.75,0:01:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁金香侵入卫星轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六十秒后到达火星南极点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体疏散  以本舰撞击!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.58,0:01:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(283,417)\fs80\fnArial Black\bord0\shad0\i1\be1\1c&HF0F4E8&\fsp-1\fscy123\fscx73}FREEWIND
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:57.04,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fs47\be1\fad(500,300)\1c&HEEEDEA&\pos(310,350)\fscy137}『像个男人般』勇往直前吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总部  总部…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概已经不行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地上啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.12,0:02:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下都如此  地上应该全军覆没了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.79,0:02:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气  我刚好要去补货
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.39,0:02:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.88,0:02:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在手动开门  请大家不要慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确保市民安全
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去挡住它们  趁这时候快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.91,0:02:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥好厉害好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  大家走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从第一次火星会战败北之后一年多来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星跟月球已经完全在敌人的压制下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球也只是时间问题罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么问题？刚人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟要我做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"史卡帕雷利计划"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该听说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在我们之中也有很多人推荐有丰富经验的你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推荐我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是军需计划吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…暂时不谈这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一次的工作场所有很多女孩子喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还有奖金
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1、2、3、4…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概有那么多…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以问你件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个数目是税后的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情大概就是这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先我们需要人材
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人材？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  人材
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的人材
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人格上稍微有点缺陷也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公啊  万一被发现的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里这么做的话莉莉就是天下无敌了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨  有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不是的  不是的  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我叫莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我当机械师？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你虽是违法改造业者  但技术不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你一定要来我们的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  去了  立刻  马上  赶快走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  条件方面的确认  还有契约书…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓  没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能够离开那家伙  就算是地狱我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么不喜欢董事长秘书这个工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是觉得没有充实感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  让我们战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.49,0:05:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  OK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有访客  自称是NERGAL的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.37,0:06:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  连伯父都生气了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这套制服太逊了  人家不喜欢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜欢也没办法呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  阿纯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你特地离开联合军来陪我真的不会后悔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为百合香一个人的话  我不放心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是阿纯  我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀  是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  百合香！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生脾气也适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  伯父  她正在换衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军人必须严守时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.89,0:06:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香  你长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为我女儿还是小孩却已经有了魔鬼身材
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香  你要全力以赴喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼近地球的木星蜥蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用拳头把它打得稀烂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家携手共同保护地球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上是政府公报
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板  八宝菜好了没有？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  什么啊  又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  又被打败了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动性完全不一样啊  不如放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这边更有意思喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小哥在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  必须把火关了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是到今天为止的薪水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要开除我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时势所逼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雇用了没胆量的驾驶员  这件事要是传了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很难做…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.96,0:07:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情不是这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社会上的人可不这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说  你也太奇怪了嘛  那种惊吓的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我只能做一个厨师…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再这样下去什么都做不成的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人如果一直逃避的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  我逃避哪里碍到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避又有什么不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕就是害怕嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也想尽办法在克服呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体身体身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了  为什么都是我倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.09,0:08:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常抱歉  真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有受伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如趁现在少拿一些行李吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:08:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些是我花了三天时间挑选出来的喜欢的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都要带去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.13,0:09:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉  还让你帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你还真是不会打包行李啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够包小点的就尽可能包小些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用衣物类代替填充衬垫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 这是… 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.69,0:09:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒昧的请问你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾经见过面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得好像在哪里见过你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？我倒没这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢您的协助  告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个行李箱不能放后车厢  要放后座
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又掉了东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这不是我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.42,0:10:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾经在哪里见过面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见过  见过  当然见过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香  御统百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.39,0:10:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来就认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟她确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须去确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.97,0:10:33.39,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(324,480)\fs35\1c&HFEFEFE&\bord0\be1\shad0\1aH&10&}NERGAL重工地下船坞入口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  这是怎么一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要瓢提督而不要我们这些部下？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那些人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在火星把战舰撞上殖民地的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我也理解他们会那样乱叫的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是各个领域的精英
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而舰长是在就读地球联合大学时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在统合战略模拟实习中号称不败的青年才俊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那位青年才俊在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里  这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.19,0:11:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,V
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,V？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又一个白痴？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下就抓住大家的心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们把在门口闹事的骑自行车男子抓了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要见百合香!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你是驾驶员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我是厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如您所见  他一直说些莫名其妙的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们来查查你的大名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基因资料？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.91,0:11:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么从灭亡的乌托邦殖民地来到地球的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也记不太清楚那前后的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我醒来时  人已经在地球上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和百合香相识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在火星的殖民地认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她跟她的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该知道我父母真正的死因
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:11:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你是厨师啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天开始你就是这抚子的厨师了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要认真工作喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.45,0:12:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  就是抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.72,0:12:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离出航还有一段日子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以到处先熟悉一下舰内环境
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's  go
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么激钢人  是AESTIVALIS吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢飞刃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂  你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员是三天后才登舰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一听说可以操控真正的机器人  就等不急先来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊  你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就让你们先睹为快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:13:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我凯大爷的超绝神妙必杀绝技
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人称…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯  超级霹雳无敌勾拳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好酷啊  机器人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有手有脚  可以完全照你的意思动作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是最新的印象回馈系统
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有这个  就算小孩子也能够控制
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫凯  大豪寺凯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请叫我凯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  可是登记资料是山田二郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是假名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大豪寺凯是灵魂之名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真实的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐木星人们  敢来就来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那个… 我的脚好痛啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好像骨折了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好痛  痛死我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那里的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个机器人的驾驶舱里有我最重要的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  麻烦你拿给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.42,0:14:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝是指激钢人的玩偶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.42,0:14:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都多少岁的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前敌方的机动兵器正与地面部队交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰桥人员速至战斗舰桥集合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那些家伙… 他们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重覆一次  舰桥人员速至战斗舰桥集合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要攻击那种地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂木星人在想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道那家伙是不是又在发抖了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人集中攻击我们的正上方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的目的是抚子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道就反击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用抚子的对空高射炮射向正上方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从下面烧死那些敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把在上面的军人们也一起轰掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都是要全军覆没的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的非人道行为吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:15:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长有什么看法？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经由海底隧道到另外一端去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.54,0:15:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后上浮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从敌人背后将之消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.37,0:15:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候轮到我出场啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爷驾驶机器人到地面当诱饵引开敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们趁机发动抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人热血沸腾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是骨折了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.93,0:15:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诱饵的话  已经出动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在机器人正在电梯里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想再被关起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要做个厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死在战场上我可不干
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.68,0:15:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.34,0:15:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家活居然敢抢我的激钢人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报上你的所属单位和姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河明人  我是厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香  那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厨师为什么有连接器?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是火星出身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚才雇佣他为厨师…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在问你  厨师为什么可以驾驶AESTIVALIS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.69,0:15:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人  是明人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  原来是明人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.47,0:16:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才为什么假装不认识我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你还是老样子这么容易害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么啊？ 你在那里做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.10,0:16:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是这抚子的舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我是抚子的舰长喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是什么人啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有困难的时候  总会及时赶到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我等一下  喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过让明人去当诱饵太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  当什么诱饵？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.44,0:16:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  明人坚定的意志女人是无法改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子和我们的性命就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要活着回来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电梯停止  到达地面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把激钢人还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.54,0:16:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战时间十分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  一定要把敌人引开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子和我们的性命就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这臭丫头！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要光逃啊  你这个胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太勉强了  厨师没可能会打仗嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在马上使用高射炮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出色的诱敌行动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人  我不会让你牺牲的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注水已达八成  开启闸门
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎良好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子  发动！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子  发动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:17:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要七分钟？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能再撑七分钟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生  畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生  畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我适可而止吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  好像激钢飞拳喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样只有干到底了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  我还顶厉害的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可..可是事到如今...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了  明人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.48,0:19:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么久等了  还不到十分钟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.21,0:19:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你提前赶来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方残存兵器  几乎都在有效射程内
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标  全部敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告战况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚱蜢  蜘蛛零残存
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我地上部队受创相当严重
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过阵亡人数只有五名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是巧合  这是巧合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得肯定  干得好  舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.76,0:19:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是青年才俊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人  好棒  好棒  不愧是明人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,0:19:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:19:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是来这里帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.48,0:20:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在碰到你之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.94,0:20:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是专程来找我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！我只是看到了这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张照片…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  你是为了还这个而专程跑来的啊
